title: Mon Jaane Na
subTitle: Amir, a Mafia taxi driver, finds unexpected love with Pari, a kind-hearted orphan. Their budding romance faces challenges as they navigate the dangerous world of organized crime.

title: Bhooter Bhabishyat
subTitle: A haunted house is getting converted into a shopping centre. However, a group of spirits residing in the house use various tactics to save their resting place.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Taraki confronts Parvati and declares a war against her, using her power. Lord Shiva is unable to protect Parvati.

title: Master Moshai
subTitle: A poor farmer named Bhanu travels to Kolkata to return a medal that he found outside his home. However, he eventually meets others who want to take advantage of his simple nature.

title: Avishkar
subTitle: A man marries a woman despite his father's disapproval. Later, when his sister is abducted, his wife resolves to locate her.

title: Hullor
subTitle: Two married couples try to save a grocery store from greedy realtors who wish to develop a mall in its place. However, they must overcome several challenges in their quest.

title: Fighter, Marbo Noy Morbo
subTitle: Surya, a college student, decides to exact revenge on a local gangster after he frames and kills his elder brother, ACP Bose.

title: Le Halua Le
subTitle: Sonali moves to the city to earn money and repay her debts to her landlord. She fakes a marriage with Suvojeet, a struggling artist, in order to get low-priced accommodation.

title: Sedin Dekha Hoyechilo
subTitle: Kavita's father holds his daughter's lover's friends captive and asks them to reveal the couple's whereabouts. However, one of the boys, Abir, falls in love with his other daughter, Nandini.

title: Debota
subTitle: After getting subjected to injustice since childhood, Rana decides to rob the rich and distribute the wealth amongst the poor. However, things get difficult when he gets accused of killing his lover.

title: Debota
subTitle: After getting subjected to injustice since childhood, Rana decides to rob the rich and distribute the wealth amongst the poor. However, things get difficult when he gets accused of killing his lover.

title: Cinemawala
subTitle: Pranabendu, who owns a movie theatre, is compelled to sell it when advanced technologies ruin his business. His situation worsens when his son Prakash earns money by selling pirated movie DVDs.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: To deal with the battle, Parvati takes the form of Adi Shakti and attacks Taraki with fire. Rage and vengeance ignite within Tarakasura.

title: Ei Prithobi Tomar Amar
subTitle: Shibu, a poor hawker, saves Purnima from an attack, uncovering her ashram ties and facing unexpected dangers as their fates intertwine in a dramatic turn of events.

title: Gandaakal
subTitle: A wealthy businessman stands firm against his daughter's relationship with her music teacher. However, a series of circumstances force him to change his mind.

title: Yuddha
subTitle: Agnishwar Rai, a noble officer, is stone-hearted towards criminals and gets arrested when he puts an MLA behind bars. Filled with anger, he avenges his wife's death, after she was murdered by the same bureaucrat.

title: Nater Guru
subTitle: A terrible heart attack leaves Sulochana in a vulnerable position. To ease her burdens, Sulochana's daughter reaches out to her estranged husband for help.

title: Dujone
subTitle: Akash is the son of a rich industrialist who falls in love with a poor girl and intends to marry her. Soon, their families find out and start opposing their relationship.

title: Bandhan
subTitle: After his wife's demise, a man tries to start over with her estranged family. When he falls in love with his wife's twin, he fears that his efforts to mend broken relations will go to waste.

title: Golpo Holeo Shotti
subTitle: Rudra is a pizza delivery man who lives with Anuradha, his girlfriend and an aspiring author. However, a horrific incident changes his life when he starts doubting Anuradha's existence.

title: Golpo Holeo Shotti
subTitle: Rudra is a pizza delivery man who lives with Anuradha, his girlfriend and an aspiring author. However, a horrific incident changes his life when he starts doubting Anuradha's existence.

title: Bonku Babu
subTitle: Bonku Babu has absolute control over his household, and even denies permission to his son and daughter-in-law to live separately. Things take a turn when the patriarch meets with an accident.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: To her surprise, Parvati senses a deep connection with the natural environment and realises her true form.

title: Ke Aapan Ke Par
subTitle: Spurned and exiled, Durga unleashes her vengeance upon her callous stepmother, igniting a tale of retribution and familial strife.

title: Trishul
subTitle: Born out of wedlock, Vijay grows up with deep resentment towards his biological father Raj, a wealthy industrialist who has been leading a comfortable life with his legitimate family in the big city.

title: Hirak Jayanti
subTitle: Though they initially quarrel, Jaya and Hiru eventually fall in love with each other. Problems arise after Jaya's father feels that the uneducated Hiru is not good enough for his daughter.

title: Khoka 420
subTitle: Krish is the son of a rich man and is in love with Megha. However, things become complicated when Megha's best friend, Bhoomi, enters their lives and falls in love with Krish.

title: Chirodini Tumi Je Amar
subTitle: Pallavi, a rich, spoilt girl, falls in love with Krishna, a scooter mechanic, and gets married without her parents' approval. The situation takes an ugly turn when her family tries to separate them.

title: Chhoto Bou
subTitle: A mother-in-law treats her daughters-in-law, Mamta, Tandra and Deepa, according to their husband's income. However, when she falls ill, she realises her folly.

title: Challenge
subTitle: Pooja, the daughter of a ruthless businessman who cannot tolerate any male advances towards her, falls for Abir. However, when her father learns about their relationship, all hell breaks loose.
